  <releases>
    <release version="2.5.5" date="2026-04-04">
      <description>
        <p>Batch cancel fix, CLI live display, and encoding improvements: batch cancellation now properly stops the entire queue, CLI shows a persistent queue table during encoding matching the GUI columns, post-encode size comparison uses fps-aware container overhead deadband to avoid unnecessary remuxing, below-threshold copies no longer trigger redundant remux fallback, and drag-and-drop text selection fixed on Linux.</p>
      </description>
    </release>
